T02TD3289E:33a-1: badzra h'um k'a ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3289E:33a-3: rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3289E:33a-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho ga'i rim pas nam mkha'i dbyings su yi ge ra las byung ba'i nyi ma la /
T02TD3289E:33a-5: yi ge h'um 'bar ba'i 'od dpung bskal pa'i me ltar shin tu 'bar ba kha dog nag po gzi brjid chen pos 'khrigs pa'o //
T02TD3289E:33a-6: de byung drag po chen po ni /
T02TD3289E:33a-7: rdo rje h'um mdzad ces bya ba /
T02TD3289E:33a-8: gdug chen 'jigs pa'i gang rgyangs can //
T02TD3289E:33a-9: khams gsum pa ni bskyod par mdzad //
T02TD3289E:33a-10: rdo rje dril bu'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD3289E:33a-11: phyag gnyis phyag rgya 'chang bar mdzad //
T02TD3289E:33a-12: g-yas bskums pa yi zhabs gnyis kyis //
T02TD3289E:33a-14: snying mgul mgo la dgod bya ba //
T02TD3289E:33a-15: aom a'a: h'um gi yi ge gsum //
T02TD3289E:33a-16: dbang bskur ba yi cho ga yis //
T02TD3289E:33a-17: rdo rje sems kyis rgyas btab pa'o //
T02TD3289E:33a-18: sngags ni aom h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3289E:33a-19: rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3289E:33a-21: // / aa bha ya las dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
